data.description:
***Updated Price and Seller is offering a 1 Year Temporary Buydown toward lowering the interest rate for the first year. This Lovely Raised Ranch Home boasts Beautiful Mountain Views and Open Floor Plan. Large Windows and Sliding Doors allow for Plentiful Natural Light and Warmth, and Welcomes You to the Outdoors.  The Level Driveway provides Easy Access in the snowy winter months, and Plenty of Parking for an RV or Multiple Cars. For the buyer who has an RV, there is septic disposal access on the premises. The Attached 2 Car Garage has an Indoor Entrance to the Lower Level Family Room. Main Floor Living provides a Primary Suite with 3/4 Bath, 2 Bedrooms and a Full Bath. Living and Dining are Central on the Main Floor and the Basement Family Room has a Wood Burning Stove to keep you toasty, and Walk Out Access to the Front Yard. The Kitchen provides Ample Cabinet and Counter Space, with a window to look out onto the landscape. Enjoy Relaxing Under the Covered Back Patio or take in the Mountain Views from your Front Trex Deck. Starlink Satellite Dish and Modem are being sold with Property and ownership to be transferred to Buyer at closing.
Approximate dates for New Roof: 2017, Primary Bathroom Updates: 2019, Trex Deck and Stairs:2019  This home is ready for your own personal touch!  Just off of Highway 285, a 50 Minute commute into Central Denver, or go to your favorite Outdoor Adventure.
